      <title>艾伯塔省省长警告特朗普将对包括石油在内的产品征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔伯塔省省长丹尼尔·史密斯在佛罗里达会见美国当选总统后警告称，一旦唐纳德·特朗普下周就任总统，加拿大人应该准备好面对美国关税，石油产品将不会受到豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
