    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛改组凸显私募市场的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/goldman-reshuffle-highlights-growth-of-private-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Todd Gillespie 在“Bloomberg Open Interest”上表示，高盛集团通过高管晋升和现有团队合并来创建资本解决方案集团，这是对华尔街拥抱私人信贷的认可。Sonali Basak 的华尔街快讯将于周五发布。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/goldman-reshuffle-highlights-growth-of-private-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:15:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
