      <title>New Mountain 即将达成收购 Access Healthcare 的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/new-mountain-nears-deal-to-acquire-access-healthcare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，New Mountain Capital 即将收购 Access Healthcare，该交易对该收入周期管理集团的估值可能达到约 20 亿美元。]]></description>
